 Krieg interessierten Forscher, etwas an Historiker, Politologen und Sozialwissenschaftler.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 08. Jul 2019) 0aPhilosophyxPhilosophy of Culture. 0aPhilosophyxPolitical Philosophy and Social Philosophy. 0aSocial SciencesxPolitical SciencexPolitical Science, other. 4aKrieg. 4aPolitische Philosophie. 70(DE-601)1043600700(DE-588)4033114-3aKrieg2gnd 70(DE-601)1048141280(DE-588)4076226-9aPolitische Philosophie2gnd 7aPHILOSOPHY / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Philosophy 2000 - 2014z9783110636949oZDB-23-GPH0 cprintz978305003730140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783050080918423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783050080918.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA14ALL  aPDA15STM  aPDA16SSH  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2HUM  aPDA3STM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GPHc2000d2014